[MUSIC PLAYING] Hello. I'm Robin Wilson. And my favorite holiday tip is to create wrapping paper using your child's artwork. Take a simple sheet of white paper, have them color on it, now your friends and family can enjoy the beautiful work of your child. And everyone has a beautiful gift under the tree. 

[MUSIC PLAYING]
